00:26:21,320 --> 00:26:22,400
then I'll tell you.

572
00:26:23,080 --> 00:26:24,120
It's absolutely impossible.

573
00:26:24,880 --> 00:26:26,200
Without the cold storage,

574
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:28,240
I have nowhere to store my ice cream.

575
00:26:30,520 --> 00:26:32,360
Fucheng has more than one cold storage.

576
00:26:33,560 --> 00:26:34,880
If you need,

577
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,040
I can help you find another.

578
00:26:36,240 --> 00:26:37,320
You don't understand.

579
00:26:37,920 --> 00:26:39,280
Ice cream melts.

580
00:26:39,650 --> 00:26:41,000
Only the food factory's cold storage,

581
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,280
located in the city center,

582
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,960
meets our transportation standards.

583
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:46,080
Then I'll compensate you.

584
00:26:46,400 --> 00:26:47,760
You can use the money

585
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:49,480
to rent refrigerated trucks.

586
00:26:50,600 --> 00:26:51,440
Bai Lan,

587
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:54,400
I remember back when

588
00:26:54,760 --> 00:26:56,600
we negotiated with the German expert,

589
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:59,040
you told me about the importance
of honoring contracts.

590
00:27:00,840 --> 00:27:01,680
So why

591
00:27:02,560 --> 00:27:04,200
are you now suggesting
breaking the agreement?

592
00:27:05,200 --> 00:27:08,000
The cold storage is a vital resource
for the food factory.

593
00:27:08,800 --> 00:27:10,000
I have to do this.

594
00:27:10,840 --> 00:27:11,680
Sorry.

595
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,120
It's important to you,

596
00:27:13,360 --> 00:27:14,560
but it's even more important to me.

597
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:25,760
Well then, name your price.

598
00:27:28,160 --> 00:27:29,400
I don't want to discuss money with you.

599
00:27:30,200 --> 00:27:31,040
Just leave.

600
00:27:32,880 --> 00:27:34,040
How about double the compensation?

601
00:27:37,760 --> 00:27:38,600
Bai Lan,

602
00:27:39,720 --> 00:27:41,000
I think you know me well.

603
00:27:41,440 --> 00:27:42,880
Money won't make me back down.

604
00:27:45,010 --> 00:27:46,600
Or are you deliberately
trying to trample on

605
00:27:51,630 --> 00:27:52,600
our relationship?

606
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,160
What relationship do we have?

607
00:28:07,040 --> 00:28:08,000
Nothing.

608
00:28:09,160 --> 00:28:10,320
If there's nothing else,

609
00:28:11,000 --> 00:28:11,840
please leave.

610
00:28:18,280 --> 00:28:19,120
Fine.

611
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:22,320
Since you don't want to talk,

612
00:28:22,800 --> 00:28:24,320
I'll give you a week

613
00:28:24,800 --> 00:28:25,960
to clear out the cold storage.

614
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,480
Bai Lan, don't think money

615
00:28:31,480 --> 00:28:32,760
can solve everything.

616
00:28:34,160 --> 00:28:35,120
Listen carefully.

617
00:28:36,080 --> 00:28:37,200
I won't leave.

618
00:28:39,200 --> 00:28:40,440
You are acting on impulse.

619
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:07,920
You have been

620
00:29:08,720 --> 00:29:09,880
moping around today.

621
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:23,560
Lu Dajiang!

622
00:29:32,280 --> 00:29:33,160
Ms. Tao.

623
00:29:34,120 --> 00:29:35,120
Why are you here?

624
00:29:45,120 --> 00:29:46,120
Where's Lu Dajiang?

625
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:48,760
He isn't here.

626
00:30:02,200 --> 00:30:03,160
Lu Dajiang!

627
00:30:03,680 --> 00:30:04,720
Lu Dajiang!

628
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:08,600
Come out, Lu Dajiang!

629
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,720
I'm not here to cause trouble!

630
00:30:15,360 --> 00:30:16,720
You don't even dare to see me!

631
00:30:16,720 --> 00:30:18,360
What kind of man are you?

632
00:30:24,960 --> 00:30:26,080
Jerk!

633
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:28,680
Jerk!

634
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:29,800
Coward!

635
00:30:30,120 --> 00:30:33,360
You'd better be avoiding me forever.

636
00:30:36,440 --> 00:30:37,280
Ms. Tao,

637
00:30:38,600 --> 00:30:39,440
forget it.

638
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:54,240
I know you can hear me talking.

639
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,280
We've known each other

640
00:30:56,280 --> 00:30:57,240
since we were teenagers.

641
00:30:57,960 --> 00:30:59,640
We know each other so well!

642
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:02,080
We have gone through ups and downs
together!

643
00:31:03,360 --> 00:31:04,920
Why are you doing this now?

644
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:07,600
If you don't want to see me,

645
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:09,200
I won't force you.

646
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:11,960
But let me tell you,

647
00:31:11,960 --> 00:31:14,280
smoke less, drink less,

648
00:31:15,440 --> 00:31:16,440
and don't cause trouble.

649
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:17,440
You'd better live well.

650
00:31:17,440 --> 00:31:18,360
Do you hear me?

651
00:31:23,230 --> 00:31:28,720
♪Memories never seem to cease♪

652
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,480
You'd better live well.

653
00:31:35,950 --> 00:31:41,710
♪Vaguely, we've neglected it all♪

654
00:31:41,710 --> 00:31:46,430
♪Mirage is all over the heart♪

655
00:32:19,920 --> 00:32:21,400
You can't let her go either.

656
00:32:23,880 --> 00:32:25,280
Otherwise, why not see her?

657
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,840
You never mentioned this to me

658
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:31,240
over the past years.

659
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:37,400
To be honest,

660
00:32:40,360 --> 00:32:42,160
I couldn't possibly match her status.

661
00:32:42,280 --> 00:32:43,880
She's a lady from a prominent family,

662
00:32:44,060 --> 00:32:45,690
with a grandfather
who's an overseas Chinese

663
00:32:45,700 --> 00:32:46,840
doing business abroad.

664
00:32:47,640 --> 00:32:48,880
After the reform and opening up,

665
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:50,440
her father went to find her grandfather.

666
00:32:51,320 --> 00:32:52,920
She and her mother were left at home,

667
00:32:53,640 --> 00:32:55,720
facing bullies from local ruffians.

668
00:32:56,960 --> 00:32:57,920
Once,

669
00:32:58,360 --> 00:32:59,240
I encountered it

670
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:03,280
and couldn't just stand by, right?

671
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:23,520
Later,

672
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:26,840
she followed me wholeheartedly

673
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:32,120
until I got into trouble

674
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:35,080
and fled to Hong Kong myself.

675
00:33:45,760 --> 00:33:46,960
She's had a tough time,

676
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:51,280
and we never had peaceful days together.

677
00:33:53,320 --> 00:33:54,880
I didn't want to drag her down

678
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:56,560
or make her wait for me forever,

679
00:33:56,800 --> 00:33:58,080
so I deliberately avoided her

680
00:33:59,320 --> 00:34:01,480
to let her find a better life.

681
00:34:10,600 --> 00:34:12,080
She thought you abandoned her,

682
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:17,360
but it made it harder
for her to forget you.

683
00:34:22,360 --> 00:34:23,440
But how did she

684
00:34:23,840 --> 00:34:25,560
become a karaoke bar owner?

685
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:32,160
Later, her father became

686
00:34:32,160 --> 00:34:33,440
a university professor in Canada

687
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:36,960
and brought her there to study.

688
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:38,720
Then,

689
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:42,480
she didn't want to continue university,

690
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:44,560
so her father gave her money

691
00:34:44,560 --> 00:34:45,680
to start a business back in China.

692
00:34:54,200 --> 00:34:55,440
I was the one who ran away at the time.

693
00:35:01,600 --> 00:35:03,960
Now, how can I face her?

694
00:35:12,920 --> 00:35:13,760
Dajiang,

695
00:35:17,560 --> 00:35:18,440
I finally understand

696
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:19,640
what you said to me.

697
00:35:22,160 --> 00:35:24,120
Among all the profound things I've said,

698
00:35:24,240 --> 00:35:25,560
which one are you referring to?

699
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,080
Wanting to see her

700
00:35:32,560 --> 00:35:33,680
but not daring to.

701
00:35:46,420 --> 00:35:49,310
♪The glass eaves♪

702
00:35:49,510 --> 00:35:53,130
♪Gradually change color in the rain♪

703
00:35:53,600 --> 00:35:57,340
♪Sunlight falls
onto the sleepless sea surface♪

704
00:35:57,660 --> 00:36:01,780
♪The cold mist blocks the view♪

705
00:36:02,670 --> 00:36:05,820
♪The season of blooming♪

706
00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:09,620
♪Wild flowers and grasses
cover up the slope♪

707
00:36:09,950 --> 00:36:13,800
♪Pages of handwritten letters♪

708
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:18,480
♪Years of journey away from you♪

709
00:36:19,170 --> 00:36:21,990
♪Perhaps the sky is gray♪

710
00:36:21,990 --> 00:36:26,270
♪Right and wrong doesn't matter♪

711
00:36:26,270 --> 00:36:28,380
♪Feel it♪

712
00:36:28,380 --> 00:36:34,090
♪So what if the destination is unclear♪

713
00:36:35,410 --> 00:36:39,360
♪Garden in the air♪

714
00:36:39,560 --> 00:36:43,570
♪Unrestrained and languid♪

715
00:36:43,720 --> 00:36:50,720
(Director's Office)

716
00:37:02,200 --> 00:37:03,200
Going to Fucheng?

717
00:37:03,520 --> 00:37:04,360
Have you thought it over?

718
00:37:05,120 --> 00:37:06,040
I have.

719
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:10,200
Having connections is an advantage,

720
00:37:10,720 --> 00:37:11,760
but it's also challenging.

721
00:37:12,400 --> 00:37:14,120
As long as you're determined,

722
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:16,360
I can hand over this project to you.

723
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:20,080
Are you questioning my ability?

724
00:37:22,520 --> 00:37:24,080
I'm just understanding your weaknesses.

725
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:26,760
I'll prove it to you that

726
00:37:27,760 --> 00:37:29,360
only I can take on this project.

727
00:37:33,680 --> 00:37:35,480
Acquiring and rebuilding a factory

728
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:38,000
is not as simple as constructing a resort.

729
00:37:38,720 --> 00:37:40,640
It takes at least a year or more
to get out of it.

730
00:37:41,680 --> 00:37:44,240
Rather than engaging in something
with uncertain results,

731
00:37:44,440 --> 00:37:45,640
I'd prefer you

732
00:37:45,880 --> 00:37:47,840
to help me conquer different cities.

733
00:37:50,040 --> 00:37:51,600
Since it's so challenging,

734
00:37:53,040 --> 00:37:54,200
I want to add a condition.

735
00:37:55,840 --> 00:37:56,680
Say it.

736
00:37:57,080 --> 00:37:58,360
If the project succeeds,

737
00:37:59,640 --> 00:38:00,800
I want to go independent.

738
00:38:02,720 --> 00:38:04,440
Do you want to leave me that bad?

739
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:08,080
Mr. Huang,

740
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:11,640
you've helped me a lot over these years.

741
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:15,240
When I was nothing,

742
00:38:16,560 --> 00:38:18,480
you guided me from project to project.

743
00:38:18,960 --> 00:38:19,880
I'm grateful

744
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:22,120
and don't want to owe you anything.

745
00:38:27,640 --> 00:38:28,840
But I want freedom.

746
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:34,760
Alright,

747
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:36,000
I agree.

748
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:39,320
But if it's not completed,

749
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:41,000
you'll help me for another ten years.

750
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:43,720
It's a deal.

751
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:55,000
(Director's Office)

752
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,520
(Auditorium)

753
00:38:56,520 --> 00:38:57,400
It's regrettable that

754
00:38:58,720 --> 00:39:00,160
under my leadership

755
00:39:00,160 --> 00:39:01,240
for so many years,

756
00:39:02,080 --> 00:39:03,280
our food factory

757
00:39:03,680 --> 00:39:05,120
hasn't achieved better results

758
00:39:05,120 --> 00:39:06,880
in the tide of reform.

759
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:09,000
Here,

760
00:39:09,640 --> 00:39:11,360
I sincerely apologize to everyone.

761
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:15,800
(Hong Jianying, Bai Lan)
Soon, I will pass the baton

762
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:17,640
to a new manager.

763
00:39:19,040 --> 00:39:21,200
Our food factory has weathered storms.

764
00:39:21,600 --> 00:39:22,640
Who would have thought that

765
00:39:22,640 --> 00:39:23,920
Ms. Bai Lan, who once worked

766
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:25,520
in our food factory,

767
00:39:26,600 --> 00:39:28,760
would represent Huaxing Investment Group

768
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:30,880
and become our factory's new manager?

769
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:33,920
Now, let's warmly welcome

770
00:39:33,920 --> 00:39:35,040
Ms. Bai Lan back home

771
00:39:35,360 --> 00:39:37,400
with enthusiastic applause.

772
00:39:41,680 --> 00:39:44,120
Now, let's invite Ms. Bai Lan

773
00:39:44,120 --> 00:39:45,520
to say a few words to us.

774
00:39:48,880 --> 00:39:49,720
Vice Mayor Bi,

775
00:39:50,640 --> 00:39:51,800
why are you here for

776
00:39:51,800 --> 00:39:52,880
such a small ceremony today?

777
00:39:53,120 --> 00:39:54,400
It's the day

778
00:39:54,400 --> 00:39:55,760
our food factory is reborn.

779
00:39:55,760 --> 00:39:56,880
No matter how busy I was, I had to come.

780
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:57,760
I see.

781
00:39:58,840 --> 00:39:59,680
Miss Bai.

782
00:40:00,120 --> 00:40:01,600
Long time no see.

783
00:40:01,840 --> 00:40:02,680
Hello, Mayor Bi.

784
00:40:03,560 --> 00:40:05,240
More accurately, I am just a Vice Mayor.

785
00:40:06,800 --> 00:40:08,400
I'm in charge of

786
00:40:08,400 --> 00:40:09,620
the restructuring of enterprises.

787
00:40:09,640 --> 00:40:12,120
We'll be working together again
in the future.

788
00:40:12,480 --> 00:40:14,080
Please support our work.

789
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:16,320
I've always been supportive.

790
00:40:17,400 --> 00:40:18,640
Yes.

791
00:40:19,560 --> 00:40:20,400
Comrades,

792
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:21,640
I believe that

793
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:23,840
under Comrade Bai Lan's leadership,

794
00:40:24,200 --> 00:40:26,640
our food factory

795
00:40:26,840 --> 00:40:28,560
will definitely overcome difficulties

796
00:40:29,880 --> 00:40:30,840
and be reborn.

797
00:40:32,320 --> 00:40:34,560
The city government has 40% of the shares

798
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,880
of the factory,

799
00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:37,120
right?

800
00:40:37,160 --> 00:40:38,160
But today,

801
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:41,200
on behalf of the municipal party committee
and government,

802
00:40:41,720 --> 00:40:43,520
I want to state that we fully support

803
00:40:43,720 --> 00:40:45,200
Comrade Bai Lan's reform.

804
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:46,560
We won't rest

805
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:47,720
until we achieve our goals.

806
00:40:48,080 --> 00:40:49,040
Let's applaud.

807
00:40:57,640 --> 00:40:59,040
Let me calculate for you.

808
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:01,680
We had to give away two cartons

809
00:41:01,920 --> 00:41:03,840
of Chungwa cigarettes for the van deal,

810
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:05,080
costing us 1,000 yuan,

811
00:41:06,400 --> 00:41:07,840
and 500 yuan

812
00:41:08,520 --> 00:41:09,360
for the tea factory.

813
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:11,960
If we rent another cold storage,

814
00:41:11,960 --> 00:41:14,240
it will cost thousands more.

815
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:16,280
We've had a huge deficit this month.

816
00:41:16,560 --> 00:41:18,120
We really can't give up that cold storage.

817
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:25,040
What are you looking at?

818
00:41:26,200 --> 00:41:27,240
I'm calculating

819
00:41:27,680 --> 00:41:29,160
how much money is needed

820
00:41:29,180 --> 00:41:30,320
to build a cold storage in the city.

821
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:32,360
Are you crazy?

822
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,440
Why build one when

823
00:41:33,440 --> 00:41:34,560
