824
00:41:39,320 --> 00:41:40,160
Xiaolu,

825
00:41:41,960 --> 00:41:43,720
are you planning to compromise
with Bai Lan?

826
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,320
We definitely can't compromise.

827
00:41:45,680 --> 00:41:46,800
But you know Bai Lan's

828
00:41:46,800 --> 00:41:47,720
personality well.

829
00:41:47,720 --> 00:41:49,240
We need to be prepared for both sides.

830
00:41:49,760 --> 00:41:50,760
Bai Lan's personality?

831
00:41:50,760 --> 00:41:51,840
I know it very well.

832
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:52,880
Quite stubborn.

833
00:41:53,080 --> 00:41:54,920
But you're no pushover either.

834
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:00,200
Have you forgotten

835
00:42:00,200 --> 00:42:01,480
that you are known as

836
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:03,160
the fiercest man in Fucheng,

837
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:04,960
and the man who loves Bai Lan the most?

838
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:06,080
Think of a way.

839
00:42:08,760 --> 00:42:10,680
I once thought I could persuade her,

840
00:42:13,880 --> 00:42:15,560
but today I realized that

841
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:17,760
after five years,

842
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:20,800
many things have changed.

843
00:42:22,600 --> 00:42:24,520
