844
00:42:24,880 --> 00:42:26,080
Let me tell you,

845
00:42:26,400 --> 00:42:29,240
just set aside your so-called dignity,

846
00:42:29,520 --> 00:42:30,560
put on some hair gel,

847
00:42:30,560 --> 00:42:31,520
spray some perfume,

848
00:42:31,800 --> 00:42:33,000
show Bai Lan

849
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:34,160
your most charming side,

850
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:35,240
and ask her to change her mind.

851
00:42:36,400 --> 00:42:38,120
That's a different thing.

852
00:42:38,560 --> 00:42:39,560
Besides,

853
00:42:40,720 --> 00:42:42,000
I don't know what

854
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:44,200
